### Performance & Reliability

1. ✅ Authentication API responds within 500ms (p95) under normal load
2. ✅ System handles 1000 concurrent authentication requests
3. ✅ Page loads and becomes interactive within 2 seconds (3G network)
4. ✅ No layout shift (CLS < 0.1) during page load
