8. ✅ Account lockout after 5 failed attempts
9. ✅ Generic error messages (don't reveal if email exists)
10. ✅ CSRF protection implemented for cookie-based sessions
11. ✅ XSS protection headers configured (Content-Security-Policy)
12. ✅ Authentication failures logged (without passwords)
13. ✅ SQL injection prevention (parameterized queries)
14. ✅ Timing attack prevention (constant-time comparison for passwords)

### Compatibility & Accessibility

1. ✅ Responsive layout on desktop (1440px+), tablet (768px-1024px), mobile (375px-767px)
2. ✅ Cross-browser tested: Chrome (latest 2), Firefox (latest 2), Safari (latest 2), Edge (latest 2)
